---
title: Lemon Pepper Double Halloumi & Veggie Fries with Tomato Salad & Yoghurt
description: Halloumi, fries and a fresh tomato salad sounds like a refreshing dinner everyone will love. We’re in love with the zesty lemon pepper spice blend that gives both colour and flavour to halloumi, and adding a cooling yoghurt is just the thing this dish needs to have our hearts (and tastebuds!) enamoured.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67b2bb8ca27a53fcaa21eb06-6c282683.jpeg
